Improve ~/agent-activity/dashboard.html + app.py on this Pi. Full spec: https://github.com/piotrmasior/raspberry_openclaw/blob/main/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-04-13-dashboard-improvements-design.md

THREE DELIVERABLES:

=== 1. NEW /api/health endpoint in ~/agent-activity/app.py ===

Add this handler (uses stdlib urllib, no new deps). Keep all existing handlers intact:

```python
import urllib.request
from pathlib import Path

@app.get("/api/health")
async def health():
    def probe(url, timeout=5.0):
        try:
            with urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=timeout) as r:
                return json.loads(r.read().decode())
        except Exception as e:
            return {"error": str(e)[:200]}
    rag = probe("http://192.168.0.153:1235/health")
    llm = probe("http://192.168.0.153:1234/health")
    last_ingest = None
    try:
        p = Path.home() / "rag-store" / "last_ingest.txt"
        if p.exists():
            last_ingest = p.read_text().strip()
    except Exception:
        pass
    return {"rag": rag, "llm": llm, "last_ingest": last_ingest}
```

Response shape: {"rag":{...}|{"error":...}, "llm":{...}|{"error":...}, "last_ingest":"..."|null}

